;プ雷ヤーのABL:Ｃ感觉をみる
IF ABL:MASTER:3 == 0
	TIMES B , 1.00
ELSEIF ABL:MASTER:3 == 1
	TIMES B , 1.50
ELSEIF ABL:MASTER:3 == 2
	TIMES B , 2.00
ELSEIF ABL:MASTER:3 == 3
	TIMES B , 2.50
ELSEIF ABL:MASTER:3 == 4
	TIMES B , 3.50
ELSE
	TIMES B , 5.00
